Template: openhim-config/protocol
Type: string
Default: https
Description: What is the protocol that the OpenHIM core server is running on?

Template: openhim-config/host
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: What is the hostname that the OpenHIM core server is running on?

Template: openhim-config/port
Type: string
Default: 8080
Description: What is the port that the OpenHIM core server API is running on?

Template: openhim-config/username
Type: string
Default: root@openhim.org
Description: What is your OpenHIM username?

Template: openhim-config/password
Type: password
Default: openhim-password
Description: What is your OpenHIM password?
